      <div class="faq-list">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">What is a content automation platform?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">A content automation platform handles multiple stages of the content workflow — ideation, creation, optimization, publishing, or distribution — in one system. True automation means those stages run without manual intervention after initial setup.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
