          <div class="faq-answer">Content management systems (WordPress, Webflow) store and display content. Content automation platforms create, optimize, or distribute content. theStacc automates creation through publishing. CoSchedule automates distribution. Surfer SEO automates optimization. HubSpot does all three but requires human writers.</div>
        </div>
